1. *Struja* je nestala u celom gradu. (*Struja* - electricity) (Electricity went out in the entire city.)
2. Kako da popravim *struju* u kući? (*Struja* - electrical wiring) (How can I fix the electrical wiring in my house?)
3. Ovaj *strujomer* je pokvaren, treba nam novi. (*Strujomer* - electricity meter) (This electricity meter is broken, we need a new one.)
4. Molim te, isključi *struju* pre nego što zameniš sijalicu. (*Struja* - electricity) (Please turn off the electricity before you replace the light bulb.)
5. Nisam platio *struju* ovog meseca, moram da odem do banke. (*Struja* - electricity bill) (I haven't paid the electricity bill this month, I need to go to the bank.)
6. Voda koja teče kroz ovaj kanal pokreće *turbine* koje proizvode *struju*. (*Turbine* - turbines, *struja* - electricity) (The water flowing through this channel powers turbines that generate electricity.)
7. Moj posao je da popravljam kvarove na *električnim* uređajima. (*Električan* - electric) (My job is to repair malfunctions on electric devices.)
8. Proveri da li je utičnica u koju si priključio računar ispravna, možda je problem u *napajanju*. (*Napajanje* - power supply) (Check if the socket you plugged the computer into is working, the problem might be in the power supply.)